    <div class="widget-content">
<p>Welcome to the Food in my Beard!  I save stuff for later.  if you want to know more about me, check out <a href="/about-me">these posts</a>, otherwise feel free to browse around and get hungry! </p>


        <p class="first">This post by The Food in my Beard was published on <em>December 17, 2008  2:12 PM</em>.</p>
    
        <p><a href="http://www.thefoodinmybeard.com/2008/12/pom-chocolatetruffles.html">Pom-Chocolate Truffles</a> was yesterday.</p>
    
    
